dialog{
  id = "prehistoric.doctor_tyrannosaurus",
  text = [[
This is impossible!$0


The Tyrannosaurus that
lays the Golden Eggs is
supposed to be a myth!$0
Ohhh...$0 oh...
but everything is very
clear now.
Brillant!$0
All of this is just
brillant!$0
It must be the one who
lead to Mr Grump's
goose that lays the
Golden Eggs, meaning
that it caused the
rupees invasion.
But it looks very
troubled...
]],
}

